Student Record Book
A web application for managing student records, built with React.js, Node.js, and MongoDB.

Features  		
Teacher Authentication: Secure signup, login, and password reset functionality for teachers.
Student Management: Add, delete, and edit student records with ease.

Technologies Used
Frontend: React.js
Backend: Node.js, Express.js
Database: MongoDB
Authentication: JWT (JSON Web Tokens)

Getting Started

Prerequisites
Node.js and npm installed
MongoDB installed and running

Installation
Clone the repository: git clone https://github.com/Nishadi4268/student-record-book.git
Install dependencies:
Backend: cd backend && npm install
Frontend: cd frontend && npm install

Usage
Start the backend server: cd backend && npm start
Start the frontend development server: cd frontend && npm start
Access the application at http://localhost:3000
backend run in http://localhost:5000

Contributing
Contributions are welcome! Please fork the repository and submit a pull request.
